docs.snippet: SEBRING, Fla., Dec. 14 (AP) -- Jim Turnesa of Rye, N.Y., and Gloria Armstrong of Oakland, Calif., shot a ten-under-par 62 in the final round of the Scotch foursomes golf today to tie for first place and won the tournament on the first extra hole.
